comments: Murphy III (NOP) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Porter Jr. (HOU) rests his forearms on Valanciunas' (NOP) back and marginal contact occurs as he pursues the loose ball.
Smith Jr. (HOU) briefly fumbles the ball before legally starting his dribble.
McCollum (NOP) reaches for the loose ball and initiates body contact with Smith Jr. (HOU) that affects his SQBR.
Jones (NOP) deflects the ball OOB.
Valanciunas (NOP) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Green's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) cleanly blocks the ball during Green's (HOU) driving shot attempt.
Smith Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact with Ingram's (NOP) left arm as he finishes during the driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on McCollum (NOP) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. McCollum makes incidental hand on ball contact and dislodges the ball away from Porter Jr. (HOU) during his driving shot attempt. The ball then goes OOB off Valanciunas' (NOP) right side and the game resumes with HOU retaining possession.
Murphy III (NOP) briefly brings his hands toward Martin Jr.'s (HOU) back and marginal contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
Valanciunas (NOP) legally contests Martin Jr.'s (HOU) layup attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in Smith Jr.'s (HOU) path and contact occurs to Valanciunas' side prior to marginal leg to leg contact as Smith Jr. moves over the pick.
Valanciunas (NOP) and Sengun (HOU) engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Sengun (HOU) establishes himself in McCollum's (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jones (NOP) absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs with Green (HOU) path at the end of the drive.
Ingram (NOP) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
Sengun (HOU) establishes himself in Ingram's (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jones (NOP) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Smith Jr. (HOU) and dislodges the ball away during the rebound.
Sengun (HOU) rests his hands on Valanciunas' (NOP) back and marginal contact occurs as the rebound sails overhead.
Marshall (NOP) legally contests Smith Jr.'s (HOU) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Smith Jr. (HOU) briefly rests his hands on Ingram (NOP) before removing them during the throw-in.
